Task 01: Welcome Message Display
Objective: Create a Spring Boot MVC application to display a static welcome message.
Features:
• URL: / • Displays: Welcome to Spring Boot MVC!
Components:
• Controller • View (JSP) • Model: Not required
Flow: User → Controller → View → Output
Note: No data is passed; message is directly shown.
Task 02: Student Details Display
Objective: Display predefined student details on a webpage.
Features:
• URL: /student • Name, Roll No, Course
Components:
• Model (optional) • Controller • View
Flow: User → Controller → Model → View → Output
Note: Data is hardcoded in controller.
Task 03: Employee Details Display
